            <title><![CDATA[【[吃惊][吃惊]#女子硬扛流感10天两个肺都白了#】近日，江苏51岁的陈女士患上流感，硬扛了10多天后，在挂水时突然昏倒。经CT检查，因肺部感染多种病毒，陈女士已...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[【<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[吃惊]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_chijing-59b444adb6.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="url-icon"><img alt="[吃惊]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_chijing-59b444adb6.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%A5%B3%E5%AD%90%E7%A1%AC%E6%89%9B%E6%B5%81%E6%84%9F10%E5%A4%A9%E4%B8%A4%E4%B8%AA%E8%82%BA%E9%83%BD%E7%99%BD%E4%BA%86%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%A5%B3%E5%AD%90%E7%A1%AC%E6%89%9B%E6%B5%81%E6%84%9F10%E5%A4%A9%E4%B8%A4%E4%B8%AA%E8%82%BA%E9%83%BD%E7%99%BD%E4%BA%86%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#女子硬扛流感10天两个肺都白了#</span></a>】近日，江苏51岁的陈女士患上流感，硬扛了10多天后，在挂水时突然昏倒。经CT检查，因肺部感染多种病毒，陈女士已经发展成重症肺炎，肺功能基本丧失，严重呼吸衰竭，随时有生命危险。医生介绍，陈女士因患有基础病免疫力偏低，得了流感后硬扛，大大增加了致病真菌的感染风险，最终导致白肺。<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[话筒]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/o_huatong-0a3e80b147.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>医生提醒，老年慢性病患者属于重症肺炎高风险人群，一旦出现持续高热、呼吸困难等症状，要立即就医。 <a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:4989311313969206" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">荔枝新闻的微博视频</span></a><br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://tvax4.sinaimg.cn/orj480/6b0e1e9dly8hlqnlo8i1bj20u01hcgqi.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/0hGRb2Fhlx08bG7TnU5O010412004nz30E010.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;template=720x1280.24.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1BThihd3VLAY5R&amp;Expires=1705118599&amp;ssig=8j9C6bhf9%2B&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/XwxLeeaklx08bG7SSO92010412002HA70E010.mp4?label=mp4_hd&amp;template=540x960.24.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1BThihd3VLAY5R&amp;Expires=1705118599&amp;ssig=Kj%2FXuerCXL&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/3gDyxXzRlx08bG7SSbew010412001wmX0E010.mp4?label=mp4_ld&amp;template=360x640.24.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1BThihd3VLAY5R&amp;Expires=1705118599&amp;ssig=Ol2tU3kDPd&amp;KID=unistore,video"><p>视频无法显示，请前往<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034%3A4989311313969206" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">微博视频</a>观看。</p></video>]]></description>
